    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/ff579568758be4dd713620694c33160b.poster.avif?t=1733883356\" width=720 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/ff579568758be4dd713620694c33160b.webm?t=1733883356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/ff579568758be4dd713620694c33160b.mp4?t=1733883356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里是某人的实验室和工厂，充满了危险的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一个迷失在这里的小灵魂，躲避障碍物，打开大门，打败出现的boss，继续前进！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“门打开了”</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/214f8e1e7739f6346baa541c90dcab76.poster.avif?t=1733883356\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/214f8e1e7739f6346baa541c90dcab76.webm?t=1733883356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/214f8e1e7739f6346baa541c90dcab76.mp4?t=1733883356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1X1主要分为弹幕躲避和Boss战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >门通常是关闭的，但当你解决图案并前进时，门会打开，你会遇到舞台的老板。当门打开时，准备与boss战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“门要关了”</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/e3e9e89d7d4187e90f43cdfb2f4c5a1a.poster.avif?t=1733883356\" width=720 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/e3e9e89d7d4187e90f43cdfb2f4c5a1a.webm?t=1733883356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322770/extras/e3e9e89d7d4187e90f43cdfb2f4c5a1a.mp4?t=1733883356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你对boss造成一定的伤害，boss就会关门逃跑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稍后出现的弹幕模式和战斗将会更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它由各种性质的图案组成，而不仅仅是“躲避子弹”。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以享受被动躲避和主动战斗之间的有趣转变。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇见符合工厂和机器人主题的机器人设计。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个老板都有一个简单的策略，只需一个按钮即可控制。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然难度不高，但是每次开门关门都会出现关卡，所以你可以毫无负担地享受它。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于那些想要专注于避免子弹地狱而不战斗的人，我们准备了无限的子弹地狱关卡。</p></li></ul>",
